00:01:07.208 --> 00:01:09.208
They watch out for bicyclists

00:01:09.208 --> 00:01:12.668
Cars have to watch out for bicyclists and bicyclists have to watch out for pedestrians

00:01:13.440 --> 00:01:17.120
These are all illegally parked bikes

00:01:17.500 --> 00:01:21.580
Parking your bike anywhere on the street in an unmarked place

00:01:21.580 --> 00:01:23.799
is considered illegal bike parking

00:01:23.879 --> 00:01:26.359
Probably because Tokyo is so crowded

00:01:26.700 --> 00:01:30.920
or maybe just to institute some kind of infrastructure

00:01:30.924 --> 00:01:33.769
